{
  "stem": "9730.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I came to the induction center, sure enough, the post intelligence officer called me into his office and, and sort of gave me a quiz on, on my feelings about this thing and how difficult it might be for me to fight the people I grew up with.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I could assure him that, in view of all the things that were happening-- and by that time, plenty of things had happened to me personally and to my parents-- that I had absolutely no qualms about fighting this evil.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I first was sent to Camp Croft in South Carolina.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was to get six weeks of basic training there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after four weeks, they, they called me out and said that-- in those days, they used IBM cards [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that, that would tell your qualifications.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a sort of-- of course, no computer system-- but the IBM cards were the early forerunners of that, you know, with punched holes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that somebody had detected somewhere that I spoke German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they wanted, of course, bilingual people like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they called me out and sent me to an intelligence training center in Maryland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How long were you with this intelligent--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From-- I, and I-- I was there from January through September of '43, with a, a period in between that I spent on maneuvers in Louisiana.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I was not, I was not drafted until November of '42.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by January, '43, I was sent to this intelligence training center.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by September of that year, they flew us to England.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first, this was all intelligence personnel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we first had to go to a pool, which was a, a camp in the Cotswolds in England.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
